TPG Contact Enrichment Service

A lightweight Node.js service that runs on Render and enriches HubSpot contacts
with industry and industry category data based on their email domain.

HOW IT WORKS

1. A HubSpot workflow triggers when a contact meets your enrollment criteria
2. A custom code step sends the contact's email and company to this service
3. The service skips personal email addresses (Gmail, Yahoo, Outlook, etc.)
4. For business emails, Claude identifies the company and specific industry
   from the email domain
5. Claude maps the industry to one of 10 standard categories
6. The service writes industry and industry_category back to the HubSpot contact

INDUSTRY CATEGORIES

  - Technology & Software
  - Healthcare & Life Sciences
  - Financial Services & Fintech
  - Real Estate & Construction
  - Marketing, Media & Advertising
  - Energy, Industrial & Manufacturing
  - Professional Services & Consulting
  - Nonprofit, Government & Public Sector
  - Retail, Food & Consumer Goods
  - Education
  - Other

ENDPOINTS

  POST /enrich        Accepts a contact from HubSpot and queues for processing
  GET  /dashboard     Live monitor showing queue, in-flight, and stats
  GET  /              JSON health check

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (set in Render)

  HUBSPOT_TOKEN       Your HubSpot private app access token
  ANTHROPIC_API_KEY   Your Anthropic API key

HUBSPOT CONTACT PROPERTIES WRITTEN

  industry            Specific industry label (e.g. "Cloud Infrastructure Software")
  industry_category   Standardized category from the list above

HUBSPOT WORKFLOW SETUP

  Custom code step language: Node.js 20.x
  Input properties required: email, company
